### 6.2. 代码

头结点需要单独处理，使用 dummy 节点。这题不难，仔细一点注意节点指向即可。

```java
public ListNode reverseBetween(ListNode head, int m, int n) {
    int count = 1;
    ListNode dummy = new ListNode(0);
    dummy.next = null;
    ListNode cur = head;
    ListNode pre = dummy;
    while (cur != null){
        if (m == count){
            ListNode pre2 = pre;
            pre = cur;
            for(; count <= n; count++){
                ListNode next = cur.next;
                cur.next = pre2.next;
                pre2.next = cur;
                cur = next;
            }
        }else{
            ListNode tmp = cur.next;
            cur.next = pre.next;
            pre.next = cur;
            pre = cur;
            cur = tmp;
            count++;
        }

    }
    return dummy.next;
}
```

